Workrave NEWS -- history of user-visible changes.  22 September 2002
Copyright (C) 2001-2002 Rob Caelers & Raymond Penners
See the end for copying conditions.

Please report Workrave bug reports. Visit our bug tracker located at:
http://workrave.sourceforge.net

* Workrave 0.2.0

** Activity during a persisted break is no longer ignored.
   Instead, the timer is stopped whenefer the user is active.

** Added taskbar tray support (Windows only). 

* Workrave 0.1.0

** First public release. 

